Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your local bowling alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm trying to sort out a billing issue I encountered.

I'm sorry to hear that. Could I start by getting your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Could you also provide me with your account number to help me locate your records? Please read it out as individual digits.

Of course, it's two one five seven zero three nine.

Great, I found your account. Could you also confirm the last four digits of the phone number associated with this account?

Yes, it's eight four seven two.

Thank you for verifying your details, Jamie. Let me check the billing issue for you.

It seems there was an overcharge last month. I have corrected it now, and the updated amount should reflect on your next statement.

Thank you, Alex. I appreciate your help in resolving this.

You're welcome, Jamie. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time, and have a great day!
